#### Feature Description

Allow to add more then 3 colors in themes (primary/accent/warn).

#### Use Case
```scss
// What's in use right now
$theme: mat-light-theme(
  (
    color: (
      primary: mat-palette($blue),
      accent: mat-palette($green),
      warn: mat-palette($red),
    ),
  )
);

// The feature request
$theme: mat-light-theme(
  (
    color: (
      primary: mat-palette($blue),
      accent: mat-palette($green),
      warn: mat-palette($red),
      custom: mat-palette($custom),
    ),
  )
);

```

